title: Motorcycle rider falls off Edsa-Buendia flyover
text:
Motorcycle rider falls off Edsa-Buendia flyover INQUIRER.net / 11:17 AM March 02, 2017 
A motorcycle rider fell off the Edsa-Buendia flyover in Makati City on Thursday morning, according to the Metro Manila Development Authority (MMDA). 
In an advisory, the MMDA said the accident took place on the northbound lane of the flyover at 10:30 a.m. 
In an interview with radio DZMM, Charlie Nozares of the MMDA Metrobase said the victim is currently unconscious. ADVERTISEMENT 
As of 10:52 a.m., the MMDA said both lanes of the flyover were already passable after the incident caused congestion. YG/IDL
